Insider Activity


Individual




George Damis Yancopoulos



Dr. George D. Yancopoulos is a Member at National Academy of Sciences, President at Regeneron Research Laboratories and President & Chief Scientific Officer at Regeneron Pharmaceuticals, Inc. He  is on the Board of Directors at Cold Spring Harbor Laboratory, Inc. Dr. Yancopoulos was previously employed as a Trustee by Society for Science & the Public. He received his doctorate degree from Columbia University.



